title: Week 7 Rankings 2022
description:
Field Yates, Stephania Bell and Liz Loza talk injury updates, what players to avoid after seeing one big game and who could burst onto the scene for the rest of the season like DeAndre Hopkins. Plus, we answer your social questions including if you should be stashing Wan'Dale Robinson or Jameson Williams.
